Pre-Game Insights: The Black Stars opened camp in Accra ahead of their trip to Kumasi to prepare for the game against Comoros.The team is scheduled to face Madagascar on November 17, 2023, and Comoros on November 21, 2023.Nurudeen Abdulai and Fatawu Issahaku have joined the squad to replace Abdul Mumin and KamalDeen Sulemana.
